snippet.title: FIFA 15 - Official E3 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
FIFA 15 Official E3 Gameplay Trailer. Feel The Game. Pre-order: http://o.ea.com/23064. New features: http://o.ea.com/22269

Out 23 September North America. 25 September Europe. 26 September UK.
Xbox One, PS4 and PC powered by the EA SPORTS IGNITE Engine. Also available on Xbox 360, PS3 and other platforms.
